    "en": "Set operation mode to [[mode]]",
    "da": "Indstil driftstilstand til [[mode]]",
    "de": "Betriebsmodus auf [[mode]] einstellen"
  },
  "hint": {
    "en": "Switches between vacuum only, mop only, or combined modes.",
